            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add your <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and <strong>dried oregano </strong>to the pan with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste</strong> and <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Ordered extra halloumi? Slice and cook in a pan with a little oil for 4-6 min or until golden all over</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1673354040371-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
